Cluffjumper reflects for a minute. "Well that depends, on your ethics.
Were the good guys, but the Maximals seem to have forgoten that. They
seem more worried about their own miserable lives, and not the lives of
the poor inhabitants of this planet, whom we have dragged into our war.
I wat to see the Predacons pay, not just sit around, and train." he said
quite bluntly.
